hi Pranay,

thanks for reporting this. sorry it didn't make it into the most
recent release. please note that it has been fixed with revision
6726[1], and is available in the latest development build[2]. of
course, it will be available in subsequent releases as well[3].

/steve@...

[1] Heritrix Revision 6726
http://archive-crawler.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/archive-crawler?view=rev&revision=6726

https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/Build+Box

https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/Home

> If anyone intends to use the 'cachePercent' property of the bean class,
